title: Elegant Tabs for Visual Composer 3.3.2 - WordPress Plugin
description: Visit us on: https://www.nulledforums.org Here you can read short review for WPBakery Elegant Tabs 3.3.2 WordPress Plugin. If you know about the new version of WPBakery Elegant Tabs WordPress Plugin, please write to us via comments. This plugin is an addon for WPBakery Page Builder WordPress plugin. It works great with the WordPress 4.0 and WPBakery Page Builder 4.6 and above.
